title: The Unofficial Unofficial Guide to Game of Thrones w/Kim Renfro
description:
Sean and Aziz chat w/Kim Renfro of Insider Magazine! She's written a book called The Unofficial Guide to Game of Thrones and is one of *the* most knowledgeable people in the world about GoT. We'll talk about her book AND what we know about House of the Dragon so far... Published January 5, 2020.
